com.devwebsphere.wxsutils.jmx
Class MinMaxAvgMetric

java.lang.Object
  com.devwebsphere.wxsutils.jmx.MinMaxAvgMetric

public final class MinMaxAvgMetric
extends java.lang.Object

This is a helper class to track timings. It tracks the minimum/avg and maximum time. It's designed to be thread safe but I attempted to try to avoid any synchronization to avoid it being a bottleneck.
